      "content": "**Key functional groups**\n- **Two amide carbonyls**:\n  - `C(=O)NCC...` (amide linked to a short ethyl chain to the indole)\n  - `NC(=O)OCH2Ph` (carbamate / urethane)\n- **Carbamate O-CH2-phenyl** (benzyloxycarbonyl-like).\n- **One indole N\u2013H** (**H-bond donor**, but **not basic**).\n- **No tertiary amine**; the nitrogens present are **amide N** (non-basic) and **indole [nH]** (very weakly basic / essentially neutral at pH 7.4).",
