      "content": "**Physicochemical implications (qualitative)**\n- Likely **MW in the 350\u2013500 Da range** (fits typical CYP inhibitor space).\n- Likely **high lipophilicity** due to 3 aromatic systems + bulky hydrophobes.\n- **Low basicity / low cationic character** at physiological pH.",
